Overview

This dashboard shows Malop Connections overview related to the Cybereason Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested Malop Connections logs from Cybereason.

It shows the breakdown of Malop Connections by port type, transport protocol and direction. It presents the distribution of Malop Connections events across creation time. The dashboard also includes the top 10 Malop Connections by Sum of Transmitted and Received Bytes. In addition, it illustrates the essential details of Malop Connections.
